HEADWORD: Calends
<hw>Cal"ends</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>kalendes</ets> month, calends, AS. <ets>calend</ets> month, fr. L.
<ets>calendae</ets>; akin to <ets>calare</ets> to call, proclaim, Gr.
<?/<?/<?/<?/<?/<?/. CF. <er>Claim</er>.]</ety> <def>The first day of
